title: Perrie Edwards forgives ex-fiancé Zayn Malik for dumping her over text because she has found 'healthy love' with Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain

description: Tenecteplase, which breaks up blood clots and prevents further clotting after a stroke, will now be given to patients nationwide after it received the green light from the NHS spending watchdog
title: New clot-busting drug that can quickly restore blood flow in stroke sufferers set to save lives of thousands of patients

description: The drummer of Pink Floyd, has said there is no way band members David Gilmour and Roger Waters will ever be friends again, after their decades-long feud.
title: Pink Floyd's Nick Mason claims band members David Gilmour and Roger Waters will never be friends again - but believes AI could create songs instead

description:

title: Coco Gauff reveals why her entire team LEFT the Olympic Village for a hotel
